column31: Post: Breastfeeding Exclusively Reduces Autism Risk Significantly “The idea of ‘preventing’ or ‘avoiding’ Autism gets parents all up in arms. It’s an uncomfortable topic, and many parents feel guilt or shame for their child’s condition. Many parents argue that Autism is primarily genetic and unavoidable, case closed. If you bring up vaccines, good luck. However, we have data that shows that breastfeeding exclusively for more than 6 months reduces your child’s risk of Autism by 2.5 times. The study found that infant formula without DHA increased one’s odds of ASD by 4.4 times over exclusive breastfeeding. When looking at regression only, it bumped up to more than 12 times the risk! Well, why is it so uncomfortable to shake the genetic narrative? The idea that breastfeeding exclusively, no formula supplementation, significantly reduces your child’s risk for autism shatters the idea that autism is solely caused in the womb. It destroys the narrative that autism is unavoidable. Every scientific study I come across acknowledges the contribution of the environment, specifically environmental toxins in the formation of autism. Why can’t we use this information to educate and support breastfeeding mothers? Breastmilk contains antioxidants like vitamin C and E and enzymes, including superoxide dismutase, catalase, and glutathione peroxidase. These are known to protect against the potentially-harmful effects of oxidative stress. column35: Vaccination Decisions
column36:
Let it be known: there is evidence that vaccines may be destroying the genetic fabric of society.
 
This claim is supported by a myriad of research, and I would like to make you aware of the widespread destruction that vaccination may be having on the health of our society. This global tyranny of coercive vaccination needs to end. Here’s the evidence that supports these claims:
 
In 1960 Australian Frank MacFarlane Burnet received the Nobel Prize for immunology. At this time he stated:
 
"Genetics, nutrition, psychological and environmental factors may play a more important role in resistance to disease than the assumed benefits of artificial immunity induced by vaccination," and considered that, “genetic deterioration of the population may be a consequence of universal mass vaccination and against the best interests of the state.”
 
2. Stanley Plotkin, considered by many to be the ‘Father of World Vaccinology,” stated in 2019 'antibody titre is not a reliable indicator because we do not know precisely how antibodies work.' As we know, many vaccinated children are still getting the diseases they are vaccinated against!
 
The human immune system is more complex than just an antibody response, and natural immunity is not the same as artificial vaccine-induced immunity (antibody titre).
 
Furthermore, by 2004 ~45% of children 0-14 years of age in all highly vaccinated populations, had a chronic illness and in 2020 this figure is now closer to 50% in many countries. Many parents are now long-term carers for children who will never reach their potential in life.
It is clear from this evidence that vaccines may be causing more havoc on the genetic fabric of society than governments have admitted. This is permanently affecting the quality of life for many children across the globe and coercive vaccination policies are also being used to control entire populations. 
 
Governments globally have ignored the overwhelming science linking chronic diseases to vaccines for three decades. Doctors are claiming that this significant increase in chronic illness in children is a 'coincidence' after vaccination. They have also ignored the well known contraindications to vaccines that are due to genetics (family history), by reducing all of these contraindications to just one - anaphylaxis. And family history is not enough - you must try the vaccine first. 
 
It’s time for the Australian public to fight against coercive vaccination programs that have removed fully informed consent to this medication. Collectively we must act to regain our freedom and human rights in health policies.

column31: You may have heard recently that vitamin D is protective against respiratory diseases. Vitamin D is a critical absorber of calcium, which means it also influences the excretion of calcium. Tooth decay is the body’s inability to replace the flux of calcium into tooth enamel. And vitamin D is the king of calcium. column31: All of us with CHD were saddened to learn of the loss of Feda Almaliti and her son, Muhammad, in a tragic fire over the weekend. Feda was a tireless and greatly admired advocate for individuals and families impacted by autism. Here are some quotes from the article about Feda and her work: --“She just was this very positive force to the world. She had this amazing personality, when she was in the room you felt it. You just felt the sun was shining a little brighter and the day was a little better, because you had been with Feda that day,” Escher said, while crying over the loss of her friend and colleague." --Almaliti was a trailblazer, friends said. She sued Kaiser Permanente for failing to provide behavior treatment for her son, becoming one of the first parents of an autistic child to successfully challenge medical providers and insurance companies, they said." --Almaliti also gave a voice to the parents struggling during the coronavirus shutdown. In a heart-wrenching interview with NPR in May, she discussed the toll the coronavirus pandemic had on people with severe autism and their families, which she first detailed in an opinion article for STAT. She described her son as “an energetic, loving boy who doesn’t understand what’s going on right now.” --“Mu,” she told NPR, was incredibly confused because his school, the shopping mall and parks — his favorite places to go — were all closed because of the virus. Almaliti became emotional when talking about how the isolation was impacting students and young people with autism. --“There’s just not enough good things to say about her and not enough to say about what an immeasurable loss this is for our community,” Escher said.
column35: Fremont fire: Advocate for people with autism dies along with son
column36: Feda Almaliti’s push for comprehensive care for children with autism, such as speech therapy and occupational therapy, helped change California law.

column31: West Virginians for Health Freedom send an educational email to all of their legislators every week. This is what they sent last night. Dear Legislator, Did you know…this past week major media outlets reported four new serious concerns about the Covid-19 vaccine trials? •NY Times 9/22: Two vaccine experts identify a major flaw in the Covid-19 vaccine trials. The trials are focusing on whether the vaccines prevent mild disease, not moderate or severe disease which are the major concerns. (1) •Washington Post 9/22: A former Harvard Medical School physician and AIDS researcher, Dr. William Hazeltine, agrees with the NY Times article. Further he notes that the design of Pfizer and Moderna vaccine trials is such that they could be considered a success with fewer than 100 people vaccinated. These are not nearly enough numbers to determine long-term efficacy and safety. (2) •CNN 9/25: The AstraZeneca Covid-19 trial is still paused in the US as more information is becoming available about 2 participants in UK who experienced severe neurological autoimmune diseases during the vaccine trial. US physicians question whether the diseases are unrelated to the vaccine as AstraZeneca claims. (3) •NBC News 9/24: Perhaps most alarming is the news that Dr. Richard Whitley, the chair of the US Data Safety and Monitoring Board (DSMB) evaluating the vaccine trials in the US, has significant conflicts of interest. In 2019 he received consulting fees from GlaxoSmithKline (GSK) which is making a COVID-19 vaccine, and he is on the board of Gilead Sciences which manufactures remdesivir. He also oversees another DSMB for GSK. The identities of the other members of the DSMB are being withheld. According to conflict of interest guidelines, DSMB members or their family members should have no professional, proprietary or financial relationship with companies sponsoring the research. (4) •In a Pew Research Center poll of over 10,000 Americans conducted September 8-13, those who say they would get a COVID-19 vaccine has dropped sharply with only 21% stating they would “definitely” get the vaccine. (5) (1). https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/22/opinion/covid-vaccine-coronavirus.html (2) https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2020/09/22/beware-covid-19-vaccine-trials-designed-succeed-start/ (3). https://www.cnn.com/2020/09/25/health/astrazeneca-covid-19-vaccine-trial-questions-fda/index.html (4) https://www.nbcnews.com/health/health-news/secret-powerful-panels-will-pick-covid-19-vaccine-winners-n1240885?eType=EmailBlastContent&eId=4556dbf9-ab9e-4e83-b0e1-e3959583d371 (5) https://www.pewresearch.org/science/2020/09/17/u-s-public-now-divided-over-whether-to-get-covid-19-vaccine/ This educational message is brought to you by West Virginians for Health Freedom. column31: A little bit of HISTORY. SV40, the cancer causing virus from the contaminated polio vaccine. Many studies say that the virus is still a resident pathogen in the human population today, and that it can be transmitted by maternal to infant transmission (in utero). https://www.smh.com.au/.../millions-given-infected-polio... The young scientists feared that DNA from the SV40 virus alone could trigger cancers. Some 35 years later their fears began to appear well founded when SV40 DNA turned up in human cancers. https://www.smh.com.au/.../deadly-shots-the-polio-vaccine... In this regard, the hypothesis that rhesus monkeys have not been used for vaccine production since the early 1960s when it was discovered that they were often infected with SV40 is incorrect. Presently, in China, 50% of oral attenuated poliovirus vaccines are still prepared in primary rhesus monkey kidney cells. https://cancerres.aacrjournals.org/content/65/22/10273 Millions of people worldwide were inadvertently exposed to live simian virus 40 (SV40) between 1955 and 1963 through immunisation with SV40-contaminated polio vaccines. Although the prevalence of SV40 infections in humans is not known, numerous studies suggest that SV40 is a pathogen resident in the human population today. https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/15202523/:=:https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15202523/ Studies with laboratory animals indicate that maternal-infant transmission is one possible route of SV40 spread. This may represent a pathway for SV40 infections in humans (of unknown frequency), as there are reports of the detection and expression of SV40 T-ag and the presence of viral DNA in cases of primary brain cancers in infants and young children. https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC452549/ SV40 has been found in every type of primary pediatric brain tumor examined. http://www.sv40foundation.org/Bradford-Hill.html:=:https://www.sv40foundation.org/bradford-hill/

column31: Let's talk about zero tolerance policies. They have been seriously problematic for many years. Why? Because they don't make any sense. Life is filled with gray areas and exceptions to rules. This is true in *anything.* Killing someone is clearly illegal, and it should be, but there are exceptions to that. If you are killing someone in self defense, it is considered legally acceptable. If it is a crime of passion, sometimes it is forgiven. (We have seen parents whose kids were victimized lash out and kill the perpetrator and get forgiven, no jail time.) And of course, with much less serious issues, there are even more exceptions and nuances and gray areas to account for. This is particularly true within public institutions where everyone deserves equal access, but not everyone has equal needs or situations. It's important to remember this -- literally in ANYTHING there are exceptions and unusual circumstances. But zero-tolerance policies refuse to account for that. They have a hard-line stance on whatever issue and the punishment is the same across the board. It doesn't matter who the person was, or what the situation was, or the intent -- so someone can be punished for following the spirit of the law even if they mistakenly didn't follow the letter. Twenty years or so ago, an honors student brought a small knife to school in her lunch bag for the sole purpose of cutting up her apple. Despite that the rule against knives had been enacted to prevent the use of weapons/threats on school ground, it was "zero tolerance" so she was suspended for it. Today, there is often "zero tolerance" for people who do not get every vaccine...or wear a mask...or various other things. People are defending all kinds of zero-tolerance policies. We need to stop this, and instead, realize that people have many different situations, feelings, needs, and seek to understand them instead of forcing them into this or that. But no. Twenty or so years of zero tolerance policies has led to a society with zero tolerance for anyone or anything that doesn't do what the powers-that-be want...today. This is why we fight for medical freedom...and speak out...and bring important issues to light. It's too important not to discuss. We are on a bad trajectory, as a society, and it needs to turn around.

column31: Remember that video of the woman who was tased and arrested for refusing to wear a mask at an outdoor stadium? Here's the whole story, according to the media and her lawyer: the school resource officer approached her and told her she needed to wear a mask. She replied she has asthma and cannot do so. He told her she needed to leave then. She did not. So he grabbed her, tased her, and forcibly handcuffed and walked her out. There really wasn't more to this story. There was not ANYTHING justifiable in the officer's use of force! (Not that there would have been either way -- she didn't have a weapon, she didn't make any threats, her only "crime" was sitting in an outdoor location, socially distanced from non-family members, and not wearing a mask.) She's now being charged with criminal trespassing. That older woman who was the only one to try to actually help her? She's being charged too, with obstructing an arrest. That guy in the white shirt, who watched the whole thing unfold, then slowly ambled over most of the way through the conflict? He's the president of the school board. And our amazing governor said that no one should be judging the school resource officer, and he didn't see anything wrong here! That it is all "necessary" to keep people safe at outdoor sporting events. And that he's not aware of "any other such incidents," like that makes this one better. Beware of sharing the video or articles claiming the woman was arrested for not wearing a mask, though -- Facebook already claims that it's "fake news." Never mind that the incident would not have occurred if she hadn't been wearing a mask. They are twisting it on the technicality of her legal charges. Absolutely disgusting, all the way around.

column31: The Milgram experiment. After Nazi Germany happened, the world was shaken to its core. How could something like actually go on? How could so many people be complicit? Most people wanted to believe that it happened because Germans were particularly weak-minded, obedient people, and that *they* would not have reacted the same way to pressure to commit unspeakable acts. Stanley Milgram set out to study the phenomenon of obedience by setting up an experiment. He asked volunteers to come in and "teach" other "volunteers" (who were part of the experiment), and if they got an answer wrong, deliver an electric shock -- one that would increase significantly over time. Milgram, as well as several grad students and other psychologists, felt that it would be a bell curve -- very few would refuse to participate at all, and very few would go all the way, while most would abandon the experiment somewhere in the middle once they realized they were hurting the other person. The volunteers were given a mild electric shock themselves first so they would understand what they were doing. Then, an authority figure stood there and encouraged them to shock the subject every time an answer was wrong -- starting at 15 volts, and ending at 450 (which is lethal). 65% of people, with encouragement from authority, went all the way to 450 and "killed" the subject. They were stunned and horrified. They tried it again...this time, with the subject protesting mildly, and eventually screaming and pleading for the shocks to stop, then falling into ominous silence. Still, most people kept obeying authority and delivered the shocks to a lethal level. Most felt tortured at a certain point...crying and weakly protesting, but they still did it. They repeated it again, in another location, and just under 50% of people still delivered lethal shocks. The experiment ended there. Even when they had tried to deter people from following authority, most had not done so. It was much easier to get them to be obedient -- even if the results were fatal -- than to get them to question what was going on, think for themselves, and refuse to cause harm to others. This explains why, no matter *what* our government does, many people will simply obey...and think that they are moral and good. It doesn't actually matter what the orders *are* or why they are enacted (they don't need a good reason), it just matters that an authority figure said so. Compliance seems the most ethical option...even when it clearly isn't. It also explains why people are so eager to call tip lines and turn others in, mock and belittle those who do not comply, and generally bully. Authority said it was okay! They are in the right, and those who refuse are not! It's scary...but it's true.

column31: We've seen this floating around the last couple of days, so let's talk about it. The implication here is that formula is both easier and cheaper than breastfeeding, so it's an obvious choice. Perhaps it was for this mother, and that's her business, but she's presenting an unfair and wrong picture, which could do harm to new mothers who may want to breastfeed. This meme doesn't look at the overall health benefits of breast or formula, and no, they're not the same. Breast milk is not "just food," it is a living immune system. That isn't replicated anywhere. There's also the fact that for most breastfeeding moms, you can feed your baby any time, anywhere, with no preparation and no clean up. Bottles require purchasing supplies, mixing and pouring, cleaning and sterilizing.... We can still do better by increasing access to donor milk for moms who can't breastfeed, offering better support to moms who do want to, and working to create better formulas as well. We still need options for everyone! But this...is a silly approach. It frames the decision in a completely inaccurate way. That needs challenged, so that new moms are not swayed by this nonsense, and have a complete picture of the pros and cons and the support they need to do the best they can.

column31: The MMRV vaccine (Measles, Mumps & Rubella & Varicella). Some key things from the vaccine insert. *Vaccine recipients should attempt to avoid, whenever possible, close association with high-risk individuals susceptible to varicella for up to 6 weeks following vaccination. This means that recently vaccinated children should be staying away from newborns, elderly, and the immunocompromised. This is barely mentioned at wellness visits. *This product also contains residual components of MRC-5 cells including DNA and protein (aborted fetal cells), recombinant human albumin, bovine serum albumin and other buffer and media ingredients. *Cases of aseptic meningitis have been reported following measles, mumps, and rubella vaccination. *Few of the MANY adverse reactions: MEASLES! Can you believe it? Upper respiratory infection, viral infection, viral rash, measles like rash, varicella like lash, gastroenteritis, ear infection/otitis, irritability, sleep disorder, febrile seizures, dermatitis, eczema, diarrhoea, vomiting. *Adverse experiences reported with post-marketing - Infections and infestations: Cellulitis, skin infection, VARICELLA (vaccine strain) Nervous system disorders: acute disseminated encephalomyelitis (ADEM), afebrile convulsions or seizures, Bell’s palsy, cerebrovascular accident, dizziness, dream abnormality, encephalitis, encephalopathy, Guillain-Barré syndrome, MEASLES inclusion body encephalitis, transverse myelitis, sclerosing panencephalitis (brain inflammation). I believe in informed consent. ALWAYS. Consent that is granted in full knowledge of the possible risks and benefits. Vaccine inserts should ALWAYS be available, and always be given prior to any vaccination appointment. https://apps.medicines.org.au/files/mkpproqu.pdf?fbclid=IwAR1ODbCJSnYkbDVJzYTrYXuJ8Y4euLtB6NsOqtNxOOSDe3bO-tiOO06Eet4

column31: In the early 1900s, when allopathy was in its infancy, Rockefeller started spreading it all over the world -- including taking it to China. The Chinese doctors, who practiced Traditional Chinese Medicine, using herbs, were initially quite interested in what Rockefeller had to say. They wanted to increase their knowledge and do better for their patients, and incorporate these new ideas into their practice. But they soon learned that Rockefeller didn't want to marry TCM and allopathy...he wanted to *take over* and force them to use *only* allopathy. Suddenly, they weren't very interested anymore. This is how we feel today. Allopathy has some good ideas, and when incorporated with traditional systems of medicine, could be quite helpful. But it needs to stop *dominating.* There are many health situations that allopathy doesn't have answers for, or has very poor answers that cause more harm than good. Rockefeller sure set the tone -- as a non-medical business man who wanted to profit -- for what medicine would become in the 20th and 21st centuries. And it's unfortunate, because taking the best of all worlds would have given the best outcome for the people. That's not what Rockefeller cared about, and it's not what many in charge care about today. How do you feel about this?

column31: How many people believe that "if it weren't safe or effective, it wouldn't be approved/allowed on the market?" Too many...as this popular cold medicine ingredient shows! The mainstream speaks out against herbs because they say there's "no evidence they work," but...there's no evidence that this drug, which has been on the market for 50 years, works as a cold medicine/decongestant at all! (Who knew they were giant hypocrites?!) Researchers aren't sure about either the efficacy or safety profile of phenylephrine HCL, even though it's in just about every mainstream cold/sinus medicine. It replaced pseudoephedrine because that is now a behind-the-counter drug (due to its use in creating illegal drugs). More recently-completed studies show that phenylephrine doesn't work any better than placebo, and it can have a whole range of side effects, depending on the person and dose. One study says: “Phenylephrine hydrochloride (PE HCl) is widely used for the treatment of nasal congestion, but efficacy at the 10-mg dose is not known for certain.” How is this acceptable? The drug was approved at a time when the only testing done was finding out whether or not the drug was lethal -- if not, it was good to sell! But they have no real idea if it works or what the safety profile for long-term or regular use looks like. This is NOT science. And it's your health that's at risk. Next time you get the sniffles -- stick to natural! column31: Science. 'The putative role of environmental aluminium in the development of chronic neuropathology in adults and children. How strong is the evidence and what could be the mechanisms involved?' "The conceptualisation of autistic spectrum disorder and Alzheimer’s disease has undergone something of a paradigm shift in recent years and rather than being viewed as single illnesses with a unitary pathogenesis and pathophysiology they are increasingly considered to be heterogeneous syndromes with a complex multifactorial aetiopathogenesis, involving a highly complex and diverse combination of genetic, epigenetic and environmental factors. One such environmental factor implicated as a potential cause in both syndromes is aluminium, as an element or as part of a salt, received, for example, in oral form or as an adjuvant. Such administration has the potential to induce pathology via several routes such as provoking dysfunction and/or activation of glial cells which play an indispensable role in the regulation of central nervous system homeostasis and neurodevelopment. Other routes include the generation of oxidative stress, depletion of reduced glutathione, direct and indirect reductions in mitochondrial performance and integrity, and increasing the production of proinflammatory cytokines in both the brain and peripherally. The mechanisms whereby environmental aluminium could contribute to the development of the highly specific pattern of neuropathology seen in Alzheimer’s disease are described. Also detailed are several mechanisms whereby significant quantities of aluminium introduced via immunisation could produce chronic neuropathology in genetically susceptible children. Accordingly, it is recommended that the use of aluminium salts in immunisations should be discontinued and that adults should take steps to minimise their exposure to environmental aluminium." "We also aim to highlight accumulating evidence suggesting that aluminium adjuvants can precipitate serious autoimmune or auto-inflammatory pathology in genetically susceptible people which is a growing area of concern. We will then move on to consider evidence suggesting an association between the increased use of aluminium salt adjuvants and an increased incidence of ASD before moving on to touch briefly on the safety or otherwise of vaccines in people with a predisposition to autoimmunity and a range of polymorphisms in immune genes." "The involvement of aluminium adjuvants in the development of autoimmune syndrome induced by adjuvants (ASIA): Evidence demonstrating the development of chronic autoimmune or auto-inflammatory conditions following environmental exposure to aluminium salts, and indeed other adjuvants, is increasingly becoming a cause for concern. Much of this evidence has been presented in the context of the “autoimmune (auto-inflammatory) syndrome induced by adjuvants” (ASIA), which encompasses a broad spectrum of immune-mediated illnesses triggered by exposure to medical, cosmetic or environmental adjuvants such as aluminium salts, silicon compounds or indoor mould. ASIA is characterised by specific and non-specific manifestations of autoimmune disease such as chronic fatigue, myalgia, arthralgias, neurocognitive impairment, respiratory symptoms, gastrointestinal symptoms, dermatological signs and the development of autoantibodies." "Aluminium adjuvants in the pathogenesis of ASD: From the perspective of aluminium adjuvants as a potential contributory factor in the development of ASD, a recent analysis applying Hill’s criteria for establishing causality reported children living in countries with the highest prevalence of ASD appear to have the greatest exposure to vaccine based aluminium. Perhaps more importantly, the increase in exposure to aluminium adjuvants displayed a significant positive correlation with the increased prevalence of ASD in the USA recorded over the last 20 years." "there is considerable evidence that vaccines, or more likely vaccine adjuvants, may precipitate specific autoimmune sequelae in genetically or epigenetically vulnerable people" "Summary: Evidence of the neurotoxicity of aluminium cations (Al3+) includes: an association between chronic aluminium exposure and the development of AD; the involvement of aluminium adjuvants in the development of ASIA; and epidemiological evidence pointing to an association between the use of aluminium adjuvants and ASD. There is good evidence to suggest that immunisation may accelerate or precipitate the transition between subclinical and overt symptomatic autoimmune conditions within the first 30 days post-immunisation, particularly in those younger than 50 years of age. The immune response to immunisation may be influenced by variations in HLA, TLR and cytokine genes. Moreover, aluminium exposure is associated with the production of pro-inflammatory cytokines and chemokines and with the development of chronic oxidative stress, mitochondrial dysfunction and glial (truncated)

column31: Are you a “WILD-atarian”?☺️It’s a person who makes an effort to eat seasonally, locally, & wildly—that is, unpackaged, unboxed, foraged & free food! The idea is to eat what’s around you & to practice self-sufficiency. I’m not one yet exactly 😉but I got to interview a man who is, just yesterday! 👍 While I was in Minnesota, I decided to swing by neighboring Wisconsin to meet author & expert forager Sam Thayer. (Swipe right for a pic of him & one of his kiddos. 😍) I LOVED his approach to eating. He & his family eat mostly what they hunt & forage & it was WILDLY beautiful & satisfying, even just to get a glimpse of their lifestyle. 😁 This is a pic of the wild plums we picked. (Well, they actually just fell off the tree, they were so ripe! 😀) He also showed me all sorts of things: edible “weeds” & greens & berries, how they store them for winter, & even their sawdust toilet! (Sooo much better for the environment!) I was so inspired & will let you know the minute I publish the experience on my YT channel. (Subscribe now—link in bio—so you don’t miss it! 🎥) And tell me in the comments below how WILD your diet is! 🙃Or how wild you’d like it to be.... P.S. See my stories to see Sam’s four year-old daughter’s field foraging tips! 🧡🧡🧡

column36:
Fluoride is one of the most toxic substances we come across on a daily basis. 

A recent study in The Lancet, one of the most prestigious and highly regarded medical journals, recommended that fluoride be classified as a developmental neurotoxin along with lead, mercury, arsenic, PCBs, and toluene. 

In terms of acute toxicity (i.e., the dose that can cause immediate toxic consequences), fluoride is more toxic than lead, but slightly less toxic than arsenic. This is why fluoride has long been used in rodenticides and pesticides to kill pests like rats and insects. It is also why accidents involving over-ingestion of fluoridated dental products–including fluoride gels, fluoride supplements, and fluoridated water–can cause serious poisoning incidents, including death.

According to the Akron Regional Poison Center, ingesting 1/10 of an ounce of fluoride can kill a 100-lb. adult. Ingesting even a small amount of sodium fluoride may cause nausea, vomiting and diarrhea. Yet despite its dangers, sodium fluoride continues to be a staple in all leading brand’s of toothpaste.

Researchers report a huge increase in dental fluorosis in the USA in a paper just published in the Journal of Dental Research – Clinical & Translational Research. 65% of kids in the U.S. have dental fluorosis as a result of excessive early life exposure to fluoride.

While pharmaceutical-grade fluoride is also a toxic drug, this is not the type of fluoride being added to drinking water and your toothpaste.  The fluoride that is typically used in your water and toothpaste is a contaminated chemical byproduct that comes from the phosphate fertilizer manufacturing process.

Fluoride weakens the immune system, can cause certain cancers and gastrointestinal issues like vomiting and diarrhea, and lead to birth defects.

Fluoride is a poison, and though the amount of fluoride in toothpaste is pretty small, we’re putting into our mouth twice a day, 365 days a year .

column31: Lots of people are interested in natural remedies, but are wary because they "don't work." Some of that is just a lack of familiarity with herbs -- how can something we use for cooking be *that* powerful? But in other cases, it's actually due to one of these three mistakes. #1: Wrong Remedy Look online or in a group for a natural remedy for a health need, and you'll get many different answers. A lot of those are general remedies and may not be the right one for your specific needs. And if the remedy(ies) you choose aren't the right ones, well...they won't work! Imagine you have a headache, and someone advises you to use lavender EO to calm it, but the real reason if you haven't had enough water to drink. EOs aren't going to touch dehydration. Selecting the right remedy is important! #2: Waiting too Long Herbal remedies generally work by supporting the body's systems and helping them do their jobs. If the body is already sick, then it takes awhile for the remedies to help the body "gear up." In contrast, if symptoms have just started -- or if a family member is sick, and you might be next -- then the herbal remedies can shore up defenses *before* the illness really takes hold. They're going to work better if taken earlier. #3: Not Using Often Enough Taking a remedy once or twice when you remember isn't enough. Especially if you are really not feeling well, your body needs a lot of help. Many herbal remedies can and should be taken every 2 - 4 hours during the day, along with plenty of rest and fluids. Nourishing herbal teas and broths are good in between other remedies as well. If these three mistakes are corrected, herbs are powerful and amazing and can do wonders for health!

column31: IMPORTANT and EXTREMELY RELEVANT ... Friends, have you ever wondered where the phrase, "the new normal" came from in the coronavirus so-called pandemic? All at once those words were on us, drummed up by media, echoed throughout our schools and local businesses. But where did it come from? Why was it suddenly a fact that we were in a new normal-- and declared so early on? Why was it so universally embraced? It's a twist on a 52-year-old phrase from Soviet propaganda. On January 26, 2020, the phrase appears to have come from Peter Daszak, a British scientist of Ukrainian origin, the president of EcoHealth Alliance, a US-based organization that conducts research and outreach programs on global health. He's also part of the Global Virome Project, A 10-year collaborative scientific initiative to discover zoonotic viral threats & stop future pandemics. Daszak has defended virologist Shi Zhengli, who runs the lab that it was alleged that SARS-Cov-2 escaped from, and Daszak has worked with her for 15 years. https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2020/07/trump-owes-us-apology-chinese-scientist-center-covid-19-origin-theories-speaks-out Does he sound like a good guy? Why does he get to make the rules? For 15 years Daszak been pushing the theory that people who "eat bushmeat" are going to bring disease to the developed world. He's the Peter Hotez of Zoology. He won't admit whether the virus escaped because it flies in the face of his own agenda-- or distraction, whatever you want to call it. On March 3rd, NPR, which is itself Marxist propaganda, launched the "new normal" phrase in the US, even creating a coronavirus newsletter called The New Normal Newsletter. If this isn't programming, what is? https://www.npr.org/2020/03/03/811728989/coronavirus-cancellations-and-travel-bans-google-is-latest From there it was wildfire, and suddenly gym owners and school superintendents were cheering on the "new normal," oblivious to the fact they were championing their own destruction. But scarily, this is where the phrase really comes from-- this is 6 minutes well spent, right here. It's a highlight reel of a much longer 1984 interview by the son of a high-ranking Soviet officer. 36 years ago he predicted where we are today, not because he was clairvoyant, but because this work has been underway in the US for at least 50 years. Click to watch: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IQPsKvG6WMI&feature=youtu.be 👉 Here are the phases he describes: 1. Demoralize the nation over 15-20 years; it's the time it takes to educate one generation of students in your enemy's nation. This is over-complete in the US. 2. Destabilization takes only 2 to 5 years. Target economy, foreign relations, and defense systems. 3. Crisis. 6 weeks to bring a country to its knees. This is where you are now. 4. Violent change of power: normalization. When the Soviet tanks moved into Czechoslovakia in 1968, it was declared, "Now the situation in brotherly Czechoslovakia is normalized." This is the root of Daszak's "new normal" in January. It is a Soviet propaganda term. Step 4 will eliminate the free market. This is our "new normal" today-- notice that Walmart was never subject to the closures that mom and pop stores were? 45% of small businesses reported being in poor financial health, as of July. https://www.uschamber.com/report/july-2020-small-business-coronavirus-impact-poll The normalization stage may last indefinitely. column31: Aware friends, today, let's talk the Immune System and Molds. Many clients will scan for molds and/or have symptoms of mold toxicity and perhaps not even know the connection. Having these assessed and cleared by a skilled root cause practitioner will be important for short and long terms healing. Our immune systems protect us from dangerous pathogens, like bacteria, including Lyme’s Borrelia burgdorferi, parasites, viruses, and fungi (including mold). It shields us from the harmful substances we encounter, including environmental toxins, heavy metals, biotoxins, and more. White blood cells, called lymphocytes, carry out adaptive immune responses. There are two broad classes of these responses: cell-mediated immune responses and antibody responses. They are carried out by different types of lymphocytes, called T cells and B cells, respectively. In the cell-mediated immune response, activated T cells take direct action against foreign antigens. T cells might kill an infected or toxic host cell. Or, the T cell might produce a signal molecule that activates macrophages which engulf and destroy invaders, toxins, and cellular debris. Activated B cells secrete antibodies–proteins called immunoglobulins. The antibodies circulate in the system, where they bind specifically to the foreign antigens, inactivating the mold biotoxins. As a result, the biotoxins can no longer bind to receptors on host cells. Mycotoxin exposure comes from ingestion, dermal transmission, and inhalation. Mold toxins are extremely potent and often affect nearly every organ system in the body. Just as it quality checks red blood cells, your spleen can identify unwelcome pathogens in your blood. In conjunction with the lymph nodes, it creates an organized force of defender cells called lymphocytes. Lymphocytes are specific white blood cells that produce antibodies. +Lymph Nodes These are nodes, vessels, and tissues located throughout the body, including in the neck, armpits, abdomen, and groin. The lymph nodes help break down harmful germs. Also, they filter toxins for removal from the body in lymph fluid. White blood cells contained in the lymph nodes help fight infection. +Bone Marrow Bone marrow is the spongy tissue located inside some of the bones in the body, such as the hip and thigh bones. Bone marrow makes 200 billion new red blood cells every day.3 It also produces white blood cells and platelets. If the bone marrow isn’t functioning well and produces abnormal white blood cells, those cells may be unable to fight infection. +White Blood Cells The bone marrow produces white blood cells, or leukocytes. These are crucial for a healthy immune system. They fight and protect against infections. They are stored in the spleen, the bone marrow, and the lymph nodes. White blood cells can circulate throughout the body. They collect in areas where there is an infection. +Mycotoxins can significantly impair the antibody production of the adaptive immune system. column31: Friends, have you seen this?! UPDATE: simply click the eyeball below to see the video. When the "fact checkers" flag it - you know it's true. Tucker Carlson reports that a top virologist and whistleblower said, the Chinese government *INTENTIONALLY manufactured and released the CV virus that led to mass shutdowns and deaths across the world. Carlson specifically asked Dr. Li-Meng Yan whether she believed the Chinese Communist Party released the virus "on purpose." "Yes, of course, it's intentionally," she responded on "Tucker Carlson Tonight." Yan said more evidence would be released but pointed to her own high-ranking position at a World Health Organization reference lab as a reason to trust her allegation. "I work[ed] in the WHO reference lab, which is the top c*ronavirus lab in the world, in the University of Hong Kong. And the thing is I get deeply into such investigation in secret from the early beginning of this outbreak. I had my intelligence because I also get my own unit network in China, involved [in] the hospital ... also I work with the top corona[virus] virologist in the world," she said. "So, together with my experience, I can tell you, this is created in the lab ... and also, it is spread to the world to make such damage." Yan's comments conflicted with the opinion of Dr. Anthony Fauci, director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases and White House c*ronavirus adviser, who previously cast doubt on the idea the virus was artificially created. In May, he told National Geographic: "If you look at the evolution of the virus in bats, and what's out there now is very, very strongly leaning toward this [virus] could not have been artificially or deliberately manipulated — the way the mutations have naturally evolved." Other scientists have panned the idea that CV served as a sort of bioweapon or was released by a lab. Fox News previously reported on Yan back in July, when she blew the whistle on China's alleged attempts to suppress information about its handling of the virus. With a vast network of contacts in Chinese medical facilities, Yan attempted to gather more information about the virus as China blocked overseas experts from conducting research in the country. Her revelations fueled ongoing complaints that the Chinese government failed to tell the world early on about the virus' threat. Specifically, she believes the Chinese government ignored research that could have saved lives. The State Department did not immediately respond to Fox News' request for comment. column31: TH1 & TH2 A balance of Th1/Th2 cells in the body is defined as immunostasis (or immune balance) and is required for optimum health and wellness. In Natural Immunity, for example exposure to chickenpox, Th1 response externalizes the infection and provides permanent immunity. In Vaccine-Induced Immunity, Th2 response internalizes the infection because the Immune System was forced into an emergency - based Th2 response and results in poor immune memory. Thus regular vaccine boosters are required throughout life. T cells (thymus cells) are the major cell in the immune system; they direct and control all immune responses as well as immune memory. Subsets of T cells are the T-helper cells (Th). T-helper cells coordinate and direct the safest and most effective immune response. Using Moskowitz’s measles example, we know that, when infected with the measles virus naturally via the nasopharyngeal route, the body produces a Th1 response that externalizes the infection and provides permanent immunity. Fever, rash, coughing, sneezing, etc are signs of the body ridding itself of this infection. Bypassing the normal body lines of defense by injecting a vaccine forces the immune system into an emergency-based Th2 response which serves to internalize the infection. So, if a natural, viral (measles) infection results in a Th1 response, why don’t we make vaccines that could elicit the same response. Natural immune response to a virus externalizes and eliminates it. However artificial vaccine-induced Th2 response drives the infection deeper and allows it to become chronic. Adjuvants are often employed to enhance the development of an efficacious specific response. The problem lies within what type of immune response is happening. TH1 is the cell-mediated immune response that happens after naturally acquiring an infection, and then TH2 humoral kicks in with antibodies and ensures immunity, but, they work in tandom. Vaccination uses adjuvants to stimulate a TH2 response, bypassing the TH1, which puts the immune system into a perpetual state of confusion. This can kick in Autoimmunity for predisposed individuals (See the medical textbook “Vaccines and Autoimmunity” by world renowned immunologist Dr. Yehuda Shoenfeld MD). The vaccination process itself destroys immune capacity by overstimulating the humoral TH2 immune response while never engaging the cell-mediated TH1 immune response. The immune system then stays in a state of agitation, which leads to all sorts of chronic health problems, injury and death. And, never confers immunity (e.g., booster shots are required to create more antibodies - the only measurement of "vaccine effectiveness"). On the other hand, when a child naturally gets an infection a proper TH1 immune response occurs, and then TH2 kicks in, tags the antigens with antibodies and we now have immunity. No need for booster shots. "What people don't know about vaccines, what most doctors don't know, but well demonstrated in medical literature, is that vaccines shift your immune system to an immune suppression type of state called the "TH2 shift." That's what most vaccines do. They shift your immune system to a weaker, antibody type immune system. If you're injecting people with so many vaccines that you’re keeping them in this constant state that now you’re switching everyone to this TH2 immune suppression, then everyone becomes more susceptible [to infectious diseases] and no one is talking about that. Now, a lot of scientists know that, but they are afraid to speak out because their careers would be ruined." column31: Thank you Dr.KhushMark PhD 🤍 'What is a vaccine? It is basically an 'injected pathogen' whose role is to MIMIC the natural immune response as closely as possible. We have the INNATE and ACQUIRED Immune system. NATURALLY, BOTH are activated when a pathogen (invader)' is detected. The goal of vaccines is to MIMIC natural immunity as much as possible without damaging the host. The ideal way of mimicking this would be to expose the host to the 'whole' inactivated version of the pathogen without any side effects. There are different types of vaccines and one can divide them into 2 basic groups. 1. Live-attenuated vaccines - this is the live 'pathogen' such as the whole bacteria or virus that has been weakened. In this case the micro-organism will start to multiply in the body and trigger an immune response. NOT advised for those who are immuno-compromised. These vaccines include the MMR, chickenpox, shingles, nasal flu. 2. Killed-inactivated vaccines - this is where the micro-organism is destroyed/inactivated and it contains the whole micro-organism or parts of it. This group can be sub-divided into: i. Whole killed vaccines; from the whole micro-organism, such hepatitis A, polio (in the 6 in 1) SOME inactivated flu vaccines. ii. Acellular vaccines are made from 'parts/bits of the micro-organism' be it the bacteria or the virus part. These 'bits' are what the cells recognize as foreign. These acellular vaccines can be further divided into recombinant vaccines (a part of the DNA is taken from the virus or bacteria and put in other cells like yeast or bacteria to make a protein that the immune system will recognize), conjugate vaccines (where a 'bit' of the bacteria is attached to a toxoid which is a toxin produced by another bacteria), and toxoid vaccines (made from the toxins released by the bacteria). The recombinants include HPV vaccine, Hepatitis B vaccine (individual one as well as the one in the 6 in 1) and Meniingitis B vaccine. The conjugate vaccines include Hib, Meningitis C, pneumococcal vaccine. And the toxoid vaccines include Pertussis, Diptheria and Tetanus (in the 6 in 1). The goal of the vaccine is to stimulate both the innate and the acquired immune systems without destroying the host. The 'live vaccines' are also known to shed, so if someone has had one of these vaccines they ideally should avoid those who are immuno-compromised. This information is NOT provided by most doctors/nurses. Now some vaccines have no impact on the immune system or have very little and this means that the individual is not 'immune' to that disease. So ADJUVANTS are added to a vaccine. (for other ingredients in vaccines you can go to the Oxford University website here https://bit.ly/3d7jtZr:=:https://vk.ovg.ox.ac.uk/vk/vaccine-ingredients#bovine-products ). The word ADJUVANT comes from the latin word 'adjuvare' which means 'to help'. Most of these vaccines are useless without an adjuvant. The goal is for the vaccine to trigger an immune reaction that will involve BOTH the innate and acquired immune system and to do this adjuvants are added. Adjuvants come in various forms from EMULSION adjuvants (as in water and oil) to ALUM which is in simple terms aluminum salts. Some adjuvants are made form 'bits' of 'lipopolysaccharide' (LPS). LPS on it's own would be a VERY powerful adjuvant but it could also kill the host, so only bits of it are used. Most adjuvants are known to stimulate TOLL LIKE RECEPTORS (TLRs). These TLRs bind NON-SELF molecules so they help in alerting the body that 'we have an invader'. Most of these adjuvants are TLRs agonists, i.e. stimulate TLRs. These adjuvants can promote inflammation, cytokine response (chemicals that are coaching other cells 'saying' come on peeps we have a job to do here), and of course the ideal which is stimulating the innate and adaptive immune system. However, to this day we still do not know how the adjuvant ALUM (the most widely used adjuvant) mediates its effects. We know that ALUM is NOT recognized by TLRs, but what it does exactly is still unknown. What about the testing of vaccines? In the lab whenever we tested a drug we always had a control group. I was involved in researching a specific class of drugs in pancreatic cancer. Every control group had the 'vehicle' in which the drug was dissolved, this was VITAL. How would I know whether the cancer was shrinking due to the drug or the 'vehicle' or whether the mice were falling sick due to the drug or the vehicle or both? We had to test every possible scenario. It was expensive, it was tedious, it was long, but it was absolutely imperative. A control group always receives an inert substance with 'supposedly' no physiological effect (the 'dummy' group). Every drug such as the typical antibiotic through to a standard blood pressure medication has to go through rigorous testing. Part of this involves placebo-controlled studies. This means one group gets the 'real deal' and the other group gets the 'dummy', the 'dummy, being...

column31: Yesterday, Ruth Bader Ginsburg died. And although not everyone will agree with every decision she made, there is one we'd like to point out. In 2011, in the case of Bruesewitz VS Wyeth, Ginsberg and Sotomayor were the sole dissenters, writing: "...[the decision to favor vaccine manufacturers] leaves a regulatory vacuum in which no one ensures that vaccine manufacturers adequately take account of scientific and technological advancements when designing or distributing their products. Because nothing in the text, structure, or legislative history of the Vaccine Act remotely suggests that Congress intended such a result, I respectfully dissent." Ginsberg did not believe that vaccine manufacturers should have absolutely no liability for their products, and no incentive to make them better or safer. She spoke up for medical freedom and for rationality in her decision here. We will remember.

column31: Important info from the BMJ! Here are some highlights: The growing body of research documenting pre-existing immunological responses to SARS-CoV-2 may force pandemic planners to revisit some of their foundational assumptions about how to measure population susceptibility and monitor the extent of epidemic spread. Memory T cells are known for their ability to affect the clinical severity and susceptibility to future infection,25 and the T cell studies documenting pre-existing reactivity to SARS-CoV-2 in 20-50% of people suggest that antibodies are not the full story. “The conventional wisdom is that lockdown occurred as the epidemic curve was rising,” Gupta explained. “So once you remove lockdown that curve should continue to rise.” But that is not happening in places like New York, London, and Stockholm. The question is why. T cell studies allow for a substantially different, more optimistic, interpretation. In the Singapore study, for example, SARS-CoV-1 reactive T cells were found in SARS patients 17 years after infection. “Our findings also raise the possibility that long lasting T cells generated after infection with related viruses may be able to protect against, or modify the pathology caused by, infection with SARS-CoV-2,”8 the investigators wrote. “At the start of the pandemic, a key mantra was that we needed the game changer of antibody data to understand who had been infected and how many were protected,” two immunologists from Imperial College London wrote in a mid-July commentary in Science Immunology. “As we have learned more about this challenging infection, it is time to admit that we really need the T cell data too.” A group led by Sunetra Gupta at the University of Oxford has arrived at similar conclusions of lower herd immunity thresholds by considering the issue of pre-existing immunity in the population. When a population has people with pre-existing immunity, as the T cell studies may be indicating is the case, the herd immunity threshold based on an R0 of 2.5 can be reduced from 60% of a population getting infected right down to 10%, depending on the quantity and distribution of pre-existing immunity among people, Gupta’s group calculated.

column31: Plaintiff Zach Otto was a 16-year-old minor when he received his first shot of Gardasil in 2012. Before consenting to allow her son to receive the Gardasil vaccine, Zach’s mother relied on Merck’s ubiquitous representations concerning the vaccine’s safety and efficacy. She saw various online, print, and television marketing materials touting Gardasil’s safety, that Gardasil prevents cancer, and that “good mothers” must vaccinate their children with the Gardasil vaccine. In 2014, Zach received his second Gardasil injection and shortly thereafter experienced body pains, headaches, cold-like symptoms, unexplained rashes, joint pains, ear pain, and enhanced lymph nodes in his neck. Over the next few months, Zach was in and out of doctors’ offices to treat his growing list of symptoms. In 2015, he received his third Gardasil injection. Two days later, Zach was at work when his knees suddenly gave out on him. Unable to move, he called his mother to take him home. Zach’s health continued to decline in the months that followed. He experienced numerous serious and disabling complications, including chronic pain, dysautonomia, and the inability to walk any significant distance without a cane, among many other issues. In 2016, Mr. Otto tested positive for postural orthostatic tachycardia syndrome (POTS), an autoimmune disorder that can result in fainting, migraine headaches, anxiety, and a host of other life-changing health issues. Now 24 years of age, Zach is unable to engage in the normal activities that others his age would enjoy; he had to drop out of college for a time and can no longer work. He is now legally disabled and must live with his mother who acts as his primary caregiver. Nurses visit Zach at his home to administer his intravenous immunoglobulin (IVIg) therapy, which is supposed to help combat his autoimmune injuries. IVIg is an expensive and time-consuming therapy in which the recipient is hooked up to an IV for hours on end. Even with treatment, Zach continues to experience many of the Gardasil-induced symptoms outlined above and is forced to be homebound, bedbound, and remains generally inactive. His serious and disabling physical injuries, pain, and mobility limitations have also had a devastating impact on his emotional wellbeing. If Zach knew of the risks associated with Gardasil, he never would have agreed to receive it. Likewise, if his mother had been informed about the known safety risks associated with the Gardasil vaccine, she never would have allowed her son to receive his first Gardasil injection. Please reach out to our legal team at 844-RFK-HPV1 to get more information and join the fight! column36:
Leading up to the 1986 Vaccine Injury Compensation Act, vaccination coverage was tanking.

In the mid-1980s, a little over 60% of 2 year olds had 3 doses of DPT. Only 53% of 2 year olds had 3 doses of the OPV.

The public had lost trust in vaccines, and rightly so--
“Between 1978 and 1981 only nine product liability suits were filed against DTP manufacturers but by the mid-1980s lawsuits rose to over 200 per year.

The lawsuits destabilized the DTP vaccine market, causing two of the three manufacturers to withdraw, leaving only Lederle Laboratories, which estimated its tort liability exceeded its annual sales by a factor of 200.”

It was consumer opposition that tanked the market. It was public awareness of vaccine injuries and death which found its way into every newspaper. Publicity of injuries, as well as the ’78-'79 “Tennessee SIDS Cluster”, and 1982 television program “DPT: Vaccine Roulette” and the 1985 book “A Shot in the Dark” by Barbara Loe Fisher and Harris Coulter fed vaccine hesitancy by informing the public of the very REAL RISKS with vaccination.

Do NOT give up. Do NOT stay silent.

column31: Five lawsuits are filed against the launch of 5G - message from stop5G.be: Three member associations of the stop5G.be Collective (GRAPPE, Fin du Nucléaire and AREHS) and five individuals have filed on September 11, 2020 appeals against the decisions of the BIPT ** of July 14, 2020 which grant five operators (CEGEKA, ENTROPIA, ORANGE, PROXIMUS and TELENET) the rights to use the 3600-3800 MHz frequency band, opening the door to the deployment of 5G in Belgium. The action is brought before the Market Court, a specialized court created by a law of December 25, 2016 within the Brussels Court of Appeal. This Court has jurisdiction to review the legality and reasoning of the decisions, based on four grounds of law that require the Court to consider: failure to comply with the environmental impact assessment procedure; the absence of any justification of the decisions in relation to the consequences, mainly on health and the environment, of the deployment of the 5G (precautionary principle); the violation of the rules of procedure; the lack of substantial information provided to the recipients of the public consultation in relation to the real purpose of the decisions. The Court will examine the appeals and schedule a hearing within three months. The stop5G.be Collective and its members expect, by means of these appeals, that the independent judicial authority seized will carry out an uncompromising examination of the ins and outs of the decisions taken by BIPT and will overturn these decisions. These decisions were in fact adopted without regard for the countless objections expressed by citizens, associations and scientists over the past several years on the ill-considered deployment of a technology of dubious interest whose impact on health, natural resources, the environment and life in society is potentially devastating. ** BIPT is the federal regulatory body responsible for regulating the electronic communications market, the postal market, the electromagnetic spectrum of radio frequencies and the radio and television broadcasting in the Brussels-Capital Region.

column31: So many people these days are throwing around the term 'conspiracy theory’ to reject and ignore information that shatters their world view. Osama bin Laden was captured through a fake vaccination program- The CIA ran a fake vaccination program, and they had Bin Laden’s DNA on file thanks to his sister who lived in the U.S. A Pakistani doctor then identified his children's DNA in the area where he was hiding, and this information led to his capture. ➕2. Polio vaccine caused cancer- In 1960 it was revealed that some of the cells (SV-40) used to make the polio vaccine could cause cancer. Between 1955 and 1963, nearly 100 million children were given this vaccine. ➕3. False testimony lead up to the Gulf War- A young girl, identified as Nayirah, falsely testified on Iraq's invasion of Kuwait before the Congressional Human Rights Caucus in 1990. It turns out Nayirah was actually the daughter of the Kuwaiti ambassador to the U.S. and her testimony was part of a campaign called Citizens for a Free Kuwait, run by Hill & Knowlton, a PR firm. ➕4. Sugar industry funded research underplaying risks of sugar consumption- Studies funded by the National Confectioner’s Association and Coca-Cola made shocking claims, such as children who ate candy generally weighed less than those who didn't. A paper published in JAMA Internal Medicine revealed that they had been padding the studies since the 1960s. ➕5. The U.S. government poisoned alcohol during prohibition- The government added toxins to alcohol to stop people from drinking during prohibition in the 1920s. Around 10,000 people died as a result. ➕6. The Gulf of Tonkin incident didn't happen- According to the U.S. Naval Institute, the Gulf of Tonkin incident on August 2, 1964, was faked in order to gain American support for the Vietnam War. ➕7. The U.S. Government employed Nazi scientists Operation Paperclip sent 1,600 Nazi scientists to work in the U.S. after World War II. ➕8. It's not really Hitler’s skull- Tests performed in 2009 revealed that what was supposedly Hitler's skull was actually that of a young woman. ➕9. U.S. government planned to fabricate acts of terrorism and blame Cuba- Operation Northwoods was meant to commit acts of terrorism on U.S. soil to gain public support in the war against Cuba. Luckily then-President John F. Kennedy put a stop to the operation. ➕10. The U.S. government used dead babies for radioactive testing- 'Project Sunshine' tested radioactive strontium-90 on body parts of newly deceased children. This was done without the parents’ knowledge or consent. ➕11. World leaders gather yearly at a campground in California- Every year, some of the world's richest and most powerful men gather for two weeks at Bohemian Grove. ➕12. The government spies on your internet use- In 2005 it was revealed that the U.S. National Security Agency (NSA) had been intercepting phone calls and internet communications. Many companies and government agencies continue to do so today without your knowledge. ➕13. U.S. government investigating UFOs- The Advanced Aerospace Threat Identification Program investigated UFO sightings and other UFO-related events. ➕14. Water changes frogs’ sex- Radio host and conspiracy theorist Alex Jones claimed that chemicals in water are turning frogs gay. While the chemicals won't change a frog's sexual orientation, a study shows that exposure to a certain pesticide can actually change frogs' sex. Estrogen in suburban lakes can have the same effect. ➕15. The Dalai Lama works for the CIA- According to declassified intelligence documents, the Dalai Lama earned US$180,000 in connection with the CIA’s funding of the Tibetan Resistance in the 1960s. The aim was to disrupt China. ➕16. The U.S. government paid for patriotic displays- The U.S. Department of Defense spent millions of dollars to have sports organizations such as the NFL, MLB, NBA, and NHL, put on shows to display American pride. ➕17. The U.S. government's mind control program- Project MKUltra was the name given to the CIA program that tested LSD on U.S. citizens without their knowledge. Unfortunately record have been destroyed. ➕18. The CIA controlled U.S. media- Operation Mockingbird spied on members of the Washington press corps and paid journalists to publish CIA propaganda. The government can manipulate the weather- Operation Popeye was a U.S. government weather modification program that used a technique called cloud seeding to increase precipitation over North Vietnam. ➕20. column31: There are two major theories of health and illness -- terrain, and germ. Germ theory was discovered in the 1700s by Semmelweiss, who theorized that laboring women were dying in large numbers due to "pieces of disease" transferred to them by doctors who had just performed autopsies. (For his discovery, and suggestion of simple hand washing between patients, he was committed to a mental institution. Because that was a "crazy" idea.) Terrain theory holds that whether or not a person gets sick has to do with their body -- if they are under stress, how well their immune system is functioning, what their diet is like, etc. It helps to explain why a group of people can all be exposed to a virus or bacteria, but not all will get sick. The truth is...they are BOTH real. It is an interplay between bacteria and your personal health which determine whether or not you get sick at any given time. One important thing to know is, many of the bacteria that can make us sick -- even very, very sick -- normally live in or on our bodies in some place. If their population gets abnormally large, or travels somewhere it shouldn't be, then we risk getting sick. Right now, researchers don't know exactly how or why bacteria grow out of control or get into unusual locations. They do know that diet and environmental factors heavily influence this. Certain diets favor the growth of certain bacteria. "Leaky gut" can lead to bacteria that escapes the gut and causes serious infection in other parts of the body. Instead of being afraid of bacteria, or people spreading illness, we need to work on our own health first. Proper diet, rest, reducing stress. Hand washing is also key. Health (or the lack thereof) is a complex interplay between our bodies, our microbes, and our environment. It cannot be simplified into "just take this pill and you'll be fine." We'd love to help you keep yourself healthy, naturally! Just ask. :) Some research into the microbiome: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2821887/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2176045/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5440985/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5339271/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6048199/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3535073/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5960472/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6503789/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6427756/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29710488:=:https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29710488/ https://www.annallergy.org/a…/S1081-1206(18)30375-2/fulltext https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5778015/ https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6251963/

column31: While the telecom companies are trying to figure out what 5G is as they continue to sell to the public a false hype, others are already working on 6G. According to a telecom group of researchers, 6G may be about a mesh of very small antennas that will work using high frequency millimeter waves or near terahertz frequencies. The main arguments for such a network are lower costs and greater power efficiency. It is in articles that discuss why we need a newer technology that we can read the truth about what is wrong with the current technology. Indeed the article explains 5G that uses massive MIMO antenna arrays is “particularly power-intensive.” The estimate for 6G is 2028, according to the researchers, by then we will be living in a different reality and "6G systems will need to deal with an almost unfathomable quantity of data — human brain caliber AI, holograms, digital twins,". These and other applications will require "an order of magnitude more bandwidth than what 5G is beginning to offer" and likely will use some form of millimeter waves or near terahertz spectrum. I hope we will get wiser about wireless technology rather than wirelessly "smarter."

column31: Delicious elderberry syrup recipe!
column35: MyKore Essentials
column36:
Easy #Elderberry Syrup: Delicious And Nutritious
Ingredients -
1 cup fresh #elderberries
3 cups water
1 #cinnamon stick
3 whole cloves
1 teaspoon minced fresh #ginger root
1 cup #raw honey

Directions -
Put the elderberries, water, cinnamon stick, #cloves, and ginger together in a saucepan over medium heat. Once it is boiling, reduce heat to low. Simmer for 30 minutes. Use a potato masher to break up the #berries to release their juices. Strain the mixture through a fine sieve or cheesecloth. Let the juice cool completely.
Stir in the honey until thoroughly combined. Transfer the syrup to a lidded jar, and store in the refrigerator up to 3 months.

column35: Liz
column36:
“It’s been 10 years since I got a flu shot, and out of fear I got one yesterday afternoon. 

Less than 24 hours later, as I was finishing an online yoga practice with a client, strange joint pain began (wrist, thoracic spine) yet I thought, “you’re overdoing it again...this too shall pass”

While I’m saying goodbye to my client, the chills begin along my arms. The A/C was off which is usually the reason. BUT then the shaking and convulsions started. Within a matter of seconds, my entire body was uncontrollably shaking. It felt as if I was submerge in an ice bath ~ I was so cold, yet no fever. Temp was around 97 F. My words cannot describe how horrible this felt. 

Had enough strength to go downstairs and get Hubby’s help. He got me in bed with a heating pad, my thermal blanket, hot massage rocks, and my night guard ~ I was chattering so violently, I thought I would break a few teeth. 

Then the pain in my hips began. Felt similar to Labor pain, only 10x worse. I rolled to my side, along with the heating pad, and luckily that dissipated quickly. 

Once the shaking stopped, I slept for a solid hour, yet woke to feel like I got run over by a truck. 
Finally came down stairs craving veggie chips and Pelligrino. 
Hopefully, that was the worst and only episode of this bad rxn. So grateful I wasn’t driving somewhere. Would have had to call 911. 
Stay safe. Be well.”
#flushot #flushotreaction

- Via @yogasorce

column31: Bliss✨right after my HUGE fright last Friday 😳 The day started innocently. My daughter, niece, & I were tubing down the white water of the Potomac River w/o a care in the world. I had even unsnapped my life jacket to get sun on my stomach. (I know, I know. 🙄) It was so fun that we realized too late that we were parallel to the takeout point where we had been instructed to come ashore. We began kicking and paddling furiously to make our way over to shore but it proved impossible. My daughter & niece made it to some rock outcroppings. I did not. My daughter called out to me, “Mom, noooo!” as I was swept away by the strong current. 🌊 I tried to stop myself but was floating down river...fast. When I made it to a bridge, I grabbed a concrete pylon & proceeded to hug it for dear life. The warning “Respect the river” flashed thru my mind. At the pylon, I strapped my life jacket back on & contemplated my options. Inside I was starting to feel like 😱 My daughter & niece were dots in the distance but were within sight of the shoreline. Certainly the tubing company would send out a kayak to rescue them & me. I decided to stay put, best I could, & wait. 10 min went by...then 15, 20. To keep my wits about me, I: ✨ prayed (for our situation & people everywhere) ✨ breathed (breathing in, I calm myself; breathing out, I smile) ✨ spoke words of affirmation (“this is not the end of my story”) ✨ laughed (I knew I’d laugh about this scenario sooner or later so I figured why wait?!) ✨ sang songs of praise & gratitude to God ( 🎶 Bless the Lord, O my soul) Slowly the truth began to sink in. Nobody was coming to save us. I saw my daughter & niece make their way to shore, paddling, scrambling, enduring cuts & bruises. I was on my own. Time to mobilize. Yes, I had my life jacket & tube but fear was still a thing. I didn’t know how I might handle the more intense rapids just down river. Beyond the bridge, I spotted a small sandy area on shore. I decided to paddle for it w/ all my might. And I made it! 🙌🏼🧡 I am grateful for answered prayer and for the hacks mentioned above that helped me thru the most anxious moments. What helps you thru the toughest times?

column31: Guys, did you know that the concept of muscle-centric medicine is that muscle is actually the largest organ in the body? We often think about muscle as it relates to locomotion and looking good at the pool or beach, but it's actually so much more than that. It is our metabolic currency, it's an endocrine {hormone} organ, it's responsible for so many functions throughout the body, it is the most important organ system to get right to prevent aging and support bone health. It is really at the cornerstone of health. . Muscle is so much more than just this organ of locomotion. It is really important and really the key for our metabolic currency. Our resting metabolic rate, the amount of carbohydrates that we utilize in terms of our skeletal muscles, it's one of the largest sites for glucose disposal, all these things like diabetes, hypertension, cardiovascular disease, these are all dis-eases of metabolic dysregulation. All these diseases actually start in the muscle tissue first. And for decades, people have been so focused on excess adiposity, rather than the reality of being under muscled. . So, good news, muscle is actually one of the ways in which we can change our metabolic use. And when you think about metabolism, that's the caloric energy expenditure that happens at rest. It's also when you exercise and you build muscle, muscle burns a particular amount of calories, and you can increase, you actually can have input into your resting metabolic rate. It's one of the only ways in which we can change it. . You really can't change the amount of calories that your kidneys or liver are gonna burn, but muscle, as this is malleable tissue, you can actually change the amount of energy that goes into it. . The first thing that you have to do is you have to optimize your nutrition. I think understanding the importance of high-quality animal-based proteins is of paramount importance. As you begin to age, as your hormone changes happen, as the skeletal muscle becomes "anabolic resistant," which is just the inability to use protein efficiently and as effectively, you have to change your nutrition. By understanding and optimizing dietary protein now and absolutely at midlife, you can optimize skeletal muscle and ward off sarcopenia. I recommend a minimum of 30-50 grams of high-quality protein, which is around 4-6 ounces of high-quality protein *per meal. I recommend one gram per pound ideal body weight of good quality protein. . 🏋️‍♂️ Next, is strength training and breaking down and building back up your muscles. I recommend at least 3-4 times per week. I'm back to the gym since the reopening and I'm at 6 days a week for 1-1.5 hours per day. . What therapy do you implement to support your muscles and your metabolic currency? Please weigh in 👇

column31: Restrictions were originally put in place early in the year because COVID was a major unknown. How serious would it be? Who would be at risk? Would too many people get sick at once and overwhelm the hospital system? The restrictions may have been a bit much, and certainly caused serious and long-term devastation in a number of ways, but you could sort of justify them due to the whole "unknown nature" of things, and the fact that previous SARS and MERS outbreaks were much more severe (albeit much, much smaller). But now, in many places, there are MORE restrictions. And we have months of data. Hospitals aren't overwhelmed and in the majority of the country, never were. We now know that the vast majority of cases are mild. Not something that most of us need to worry about. And, although the US doesn't like to talk about it, China and other countries have been studying herbs and other natural remedies and have found effective treatments. (And...have had fewer cases and better outcomes than the US, which is relying too heavily on hoping for a vaccine.) It may have made sense once. Maybe. But it surely doesn't now.

column31: A COVID-19 vaccine trial participant develops SEVERE adverse reaction from the shot: Transverse Myelitis. "The COVID-19 vaccine participant whose unexpected illness put the AstraZeneca trials on pause came down with an inflammatory syndrome known as transverse myelitis, according to a report. The individual had been involved in the UK trials when they came down with the condition, which affects the spinal cord and is often sparked by viral infections, a source told The New York Times. The illness results in inflammation of both sides of the spinal cord, interfering with how messages are sent throughout the body and potentially causing paralysis, according to the Mayo Clinic. It’s also associated with pain, muscle weakness, sensory problems, or bladder and bowel dysfunction. The drug giant vowed to investigate whether the vaccine, which was developed with the University of Oxford in Britain, was responsible for the syndrome."

column31: Guys, as I'm bioscanning clients, which is a comprehensive assessment similar to dropping a needle on your album and reading your information (causes & solutions), it's the vibrational record of an individuals biology, from womb until now ...and transgenerationally 💿, I'm seeing a lot of hemoglobin and blood oxygen issues, so let's talk ... What is hemoglobin? Hemoglobin is the protein molecule in red blood cells that carries oxygen from the lungs to the body's tissues and returns carbon dioxide from the tissues back to the lungs. Hemoglobin is made up of four protein molecules (globulin chains) that are connected together. The normal adult hemoglobin (abbreviated Hgb or Hb) molecule contains two alpha-globulin chains and two beta-globulin chains. In fetuses and infants, beta chains are not common and the hemoglobin molecule is made up of two alpha chains and two gamma chains. As the infant grows, the gamma chains are gradually replaced by beta chains, forming the adult hemoglobin structure. Each globulin chain contains an important iron-containing porphyrin compound termed heme. Embedded within the heme compound is an iron atom that is vital in transporting oxygen and carbon dioxide in our blood. The iron contained in hemoglobin is also responsible for the red color of blood. Hemoglobin also plays an important role in maintaining the shape of the red blood cells. In their natural shape, red blood cells are round with narrow centers resembling a donut without a hole in the middle. Abnormal hemoglobin structure can, therefore, disrupt the shape of red blood cells and impede their function and flow through blood vessels.
